cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.COM 

This paper deals with the probability of erasure computation for OFDM signals used by MIMO systems, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networked and distributed systems (cs.NI), control and systems engineering (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communications (cs.COM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
